headline: Strength Seen in Vimeo (VMEO): Can Its 60.9% Jump Turn into More Strength?
summary: Vimeo (VMEO) was a big mover last session on higher-than-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions might help the stock continue moving higher in the near term.
